{{Han etym}}
{{Han compound|手|alt1=扌|戈|ls=psc|c1=s|c2=p|t1=hand}}.

Originally a variant form of {{zh-l|*划}}. Borrowed to mean a similar action.{{rfv-etymology|zh}}

The popular interpretation as a hand ({{zh-l|*扌}}) looking for a halberd ({{zh-l|*戈}}) is a [[mnemonic]] and not the origin of the character.

